data.description: Sun-drenched and fully renovated end-unit townhouse with 3 large bedrooms, 2.5 baths and spacious yard! Enjoy every minute with all of the upgrades!  A+ eat-in-kitchen with stainless steel appliances (refrigerator, stove, microwave, dishwasher), quartz countertops, brand-new cabinets, tile flooring and balcony overlooking the backyard. Washer/Dryer in unit. Hardwood floors throughout! Living room/Dining Combo! Primary bedroom with new en-suite! Attic for additional storage. One-car attached garage. Great location! To help visualize this home's floor plan and to highlight its potential, virtual furnishings may have been added to photos found in this listing.
